Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.66,0:01:32.16,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不断地奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.16,0:01:36.21,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但是你教会了我
