Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:44.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Suddenly
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.88,0:01:47.01,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的声音融化了我的 Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.01,0:01:49.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在想着没有任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.60,0:01:52.26,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\t(\3c&H797979&\4a90)}真正地了解我
