Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.44,0:02:02.27,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\3c&H587092&\4a90}回握着我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.94,0:02:04.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\3c&H0A59D5&\4a90}将誓约藏于心中
