Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.33,0:02:17.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\3c&HE99B25&\4a90}我才能变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:19.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\3c&HE99B25&\4a90}Fight for you and I
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.04,0:02:21.42,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\3c&HFD1EB0&\4a90}我不会忘却你的名字
