Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.41,0:00:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}了解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.20,0:00:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}祝你们武运昌隆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.82,0:00:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.62,0:00:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我 我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.08,0:00:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没关系 不用勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.58,0:00:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为妮娜讨厌战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.92,0:00:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.75,0:00:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以在这里等我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.10,0:01:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然弱小但数量却无谓地增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}人类正是蚕食着这世界的蝼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.29,0:03:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.71,0:03:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这不是刚刚的人类们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.09,0:03:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等不及和我愉快地玩耍了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.14,0:03:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我才没有让你愉快的打算!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我要打倒你!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是非常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}比起将成群的蝼蚁压扁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们似乎更有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}从刚刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就全身都是破绽!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.24,0:03:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}人家要上了!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你以为用这种玩具…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}能抓住我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.46,0:03:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只要能吸引你的注意就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.59,0:03:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们早就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}已经准备好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「闪光冲击」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}成…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}成功了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那是吾想说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.57,0:04:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也是 不会那么顺利的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哎呀哎呀 五对一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.70,0:04:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而且还有四个最强种 对我很不利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以让我找点援军吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好恶心…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}召唤了魔物?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.59,0:04:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}完全感受不到知性
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.89,0:04:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好了 我可爱的仆从们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}随你们喜欢地吞噬一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.14,0:04:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喵!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「龙之咆哮」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}哎呀哎呀 真是不可靠的援军呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}终究只是空有数量的杂鱼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只剩下你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但我忘了说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}它们能像这样无限地诞生出来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那就再全部打倒一次!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那份斗志真是值得赞赏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但请别忘了我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}奏!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}居然对奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「龙息」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.99,0:05:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你没事吧 奏?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}塔妮雅!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}塔妮雅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你没事吧 塔妮雅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}人家没事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.30,0:05:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真不愧是龙族
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}刚刚稍微让我享受了一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:05:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以这是那下的回礼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}城镇…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.07,0:06:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}蝼蚁们的巢穴烧得真旺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.53,0:06:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你这家伙!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「火球多重射击」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}区区人类的魔法…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.37,0:06:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「旋风神枪」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.13,0:06:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是现在!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「多重能力增幅」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是这个!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这就是雷因的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}两位 现在就去分出胜负吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.35,0:06:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}交给我们!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:06:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「审判」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}结束了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.83,0:07:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}承受了那么多攻击居然还…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.09,0:07:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但这真是值得赞赏的一击呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}居然还有这么多力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.52,0:07:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这是什么夸张的数量啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.56,0:07:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}再让我看看你们身陷绝望的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}逃走了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.78,0:07:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不 那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}他打算毁灭赫莱森
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}别想得逞!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}被挡下了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:07:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那样的话无法用魔法直接攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那就再会了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.97,0:08:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.97,0:08:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}该 该怎么办啊 雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我有一个想尝试看看的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.06,0:08:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真的吗 我们也来帮忙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在那段期间镇上的居民会…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.19,0:08:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你似乎很困扰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.40,0:08:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}搞不好我们可以帮上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.57,0:08:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}索菈?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.45,0:08:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没关系吧 露娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.33,0:08:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}用传送魔法将镇上的人们送到安全地区
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在那段期间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因你们只要打倒魔族就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因 这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.13,0:08:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没错 居民们的损害就能大幅减少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果担心我们的真实身份的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}反正被救出宅邸的人们早就已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.22,0:08:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}吾说过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.51,0:08:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}吾和姐姐同样想守护这个城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}索菈 露娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拜托你们了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.73,0:08:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好的 请交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真的不用去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.99,0:09:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然还未确认
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但搞不好有魔族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.07,0:09:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}魔族是魔王的侦察部队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么也是我们勇者队伍的敌…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没有必要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们的敌人是魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.41,0:09:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}杂鱼就别管了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没错 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}搞不好魔族根本就是道听涂说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.25,0:09:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但如果是真的该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.30,0:09:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}阿加斯 米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们对本勇者的判断有意见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不 没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是的 勇者的判断就是神的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就算由我们打倒也没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.86,0:09:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}即死魔法和被封印魔族的两段陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样就算是雷因一定也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.96,0:09:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就这样一口气打通居民们的避难道路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:09:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.92,0:10:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}像这么多的数量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.42,0:10:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}体力还能撑到什么时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}果然只靠我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}别说丧气话!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.30,0:10:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要是我们在这里倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}赫莱森的居民会怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不管是怎样的情况都要守护城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这就是骑士的职责!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.52,0:10:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}史黛拉!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}找你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}关于居民们的避难
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有件事想拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}原来如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.82,0:10:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}用传送魔法让居民到安全地区避难吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.87,0:10:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}请务必让我们协助
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为如果只由我们精灵族来说明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.62,0:10:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不知道能不能获得大家的信任
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.59,0:10:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就如你们所听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}由我们来引导居民们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.59,0:10:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要上了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没事的 妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们会保护妮娜的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.31,0:10:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因一定会打倒他的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么我们也赶快准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:02.19,Up,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样就可以了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.41,0:11:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}碍事 快滚开!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谢谢你 奏妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}龙族的姐姐好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.58,0:11:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这里就交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.42,0:11:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}请快点逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可恶 接二连三的冒出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.42,0:11:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不行 雷因要保留体力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}把你送到那里是我们的工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.64,0:11:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们会用这个魔法阵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.89,0:11:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}将各位送到安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.10,0:11:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那个翅膀…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}该不会是精灵族吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}据说他们很讨厌人类
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.65,0:11:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不知道进去那个魔法阵会不会有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.48,0:11:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.65,0:11:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也不知道会被传送到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.36,0:11:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}果然还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们有吃过我们店的热狗对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}非常的美味
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}吾还是第一次吃到那么美味的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}很好吃对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.09,0:12:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}既然会觉得同样的东西好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.26,0:12:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}人类和精灵族也没有什么差别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.64,0:12:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.89,0:12:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你是?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大姐姐你们好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们是花的妖精吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大姐姐你们果然是妖精呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谢谢你们帮助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}拜托你们两位了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.58,0:12:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「魔力传送」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.29,0:12:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}接着是第二批
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}到魔法阵里面去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}队长 不好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.38,0:12:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}魔物出现了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.68,0:13:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}传送就交给索菈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以露娜就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.35,0:13:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}吾知道了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}喵!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是的 明明一点也不强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.65,0:13:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但数量太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还有猫灵族的大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这里就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.96,0:13:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}塔妮雅大姐是让我们洗心革面的大恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.00,0:13:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}让我们来帮忙吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们几个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可不只有我们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}赫莱森冒险者公会发布了特别委托
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.97,0:13:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}请求冒险者们掩护雷因的队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}目前以他们和少数的骑士团为中心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.14,0:13:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}正在击退袭击镇上的魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.65,0:13:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只要勇者队伍不参加
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就会是一场艰辛的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}请拯救城镇…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.57,0:13:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为了帮助他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.82,0:13:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}请把力量借给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.87,0:14:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因他们对老夫有恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果要去帮助赌上性命守护城镇的他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.75,0:14:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}老夫这些倾注心血打造的可爱武器们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就不用客气拿去使用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}交给我们吧 他们也对我有恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}才不需要胆小鬼勇者的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只要有这个就能战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.47,0:14:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}赫莱森就由我们来守护
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.56,0:14:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}是吗 大家都来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们又会想办法解决的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.81,0:14:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这里就请交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}气氛好像变好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.40,0:14:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}勇气百倍…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不 是千倍喵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我一定会守护这个城镇的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}作为一名骑士 挥舞你们的剑!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「魔力传送」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}吾不会让任何一只通过这里!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.05,0:15:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「火球多重射击」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.39,0:15:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快进到魔法阵里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.14,0:15:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「幻影箭」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.72,0:15:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}别退缩 不管怎样都要挡住它们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.11,0:15:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不管是受伤还是伤害人都好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.28,0:15:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我一直在逃避着 一直忍耐着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大家都在抵抗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是我却…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只被保护着就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.16,0:15:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「魔力传送」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妮娜 你也快点去避难…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妮娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.09,0:15:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因…怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.76,0:15:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}距离太远了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}得想办法到那家伙的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那么只要让塔妮雅变成龙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一口气飞到天上的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.06,0:15:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那个型态没办法灵活行动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.69,0:15:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}轻易接近的话会变成活靶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.53,0:16:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就算从远处攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那些魔物也会成为防壁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.91,0:16:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}无法打到他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那用索菈她们的传送魔法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那也很困难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}传送魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.08,0:16:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}需要事前进行各种条件的设定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.04,0:16:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在战斗的同时随着目标的移动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}及时设定传送地点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.88,0:16:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也就是瞬间移动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.05,0:16:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就算是索菈和露娜也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}如果要说谁能做到那种精密的传送…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妮娜!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妮娜 为什么你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我已经不想什么也不做一直逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.69,0:16:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还有一直被保护着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.98,0:16:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我也想成为雷因的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.07,0:16:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}神族!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.16,0:16:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我听说神族有着其他最强种 没有的特殊能力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好像是可以操纵空间之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.21,0:16:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妮娜或许可以办到瞬间移动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我想要去那个魔族的附近
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我做得到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你可以把力量借给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.02,0:17:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因 妮娜 快一点!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这里就交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.98,0:17:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是这个数量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就算是你们两个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.19,0:17:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}因为我们相信着你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我们的主人一定会想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.75,0:17:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}区区的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只有一只打算做些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}到处乱窜…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.31,0:17:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是你能躲开这招吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.15,0:18:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「传送」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.37,0:18:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.04,0:18:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}又见面了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.33,0:18:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}为 为什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那家伙是…神族!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}原来如此 这是瞬间移动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.01,0:18:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而且连续使用的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就能做到类似飞行的移动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.68,0:18:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}软弱的人类能做到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.02,0:18:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}「能力增幅」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.40,0:18:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}力量增幅?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}区区的人类就算增幅了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.86,0:18:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}又有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不过能接近我倒是得夸奖你一番
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但这下就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}吞噬那个人类吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}能增幅的能力…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:18:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可不只有身体能力而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.25,0:19:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你这家伙…要做什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因! 雷因!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.06,0:19:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}分身们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.48,0:19:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}将这些家伙吞噬!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.69,0:19:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}服从我吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你…你们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快点吞噬这个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.55,0:19:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你对你的魔物们的支配权
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.59,0:19:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}已经被我覆盖了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.47,0:19:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}夺走我的支配权什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.85,0:19:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.68,0:19:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而且还是区区的人类…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.10,0:20:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你是什么人!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.64,0:20:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}只是个驭兽使而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}驭兽使?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.11,0:20:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}区区的驭兽使为何能使役我的魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.82,0:20:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}上吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.78,0:20:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我一个人的话是做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.49,0:20:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但只要和同伴们一起的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}去死吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就能够打倒你!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然是预料之外
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但这种结局也挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}人类 能告诉我你的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:20:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:21:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是冷漠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.29,0:21:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}结束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.29,0:21:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.54,0:21:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}谢谢 多亏了你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}已经…不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}塔妮雅!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}真是的 在最后掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.10,0:21:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}奏!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}还有大家!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然并不是完全平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}一定也有受伤的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.07,0:21:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但是我成功守护住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.67,0:21:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}在那之后过了三天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}镇上已经渐渐取回了过往的活力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.55,0:21:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}赫莱森非常地坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.22,0:21:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}史黛拉正式就任为骑士团的新队长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.51,0:22:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}想必她一定能让骑士团重获新生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.85,0:22:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}据史黛拉所说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.85,0:22:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}那些有不法勾结的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.81,0:22:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}都被送往了王都等候裁决
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.40,0:22:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}此外 她也调查了妮娜村庄的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.40,0:22:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}据说村民们在失去妮娜后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.03,0:22:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就离开了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.70,0:22:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但只要还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.66,0:22:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}总有一天还会相见的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.75,0:22:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}奏在镇上的复兴工作大展身手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.42,0:22:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}已经完全融入赫莱森了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.88,0:22:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}虽然塔妮雅隐瞒了自己是龙族这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.35,0:22:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}但大家好像好久以前就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.77,0:22:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}索菈和露娜也逐渐熟悉了镇上的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.03,0:22:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}小姐你们辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.15,0:22:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}刚做好的 趁热吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.54,0:23:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}要吃多少都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.45,0:23:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.66,0:23:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}你们正是这镇上的英雄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.67,0:23:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}都是因为大家很厉害的关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.21,0:23:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不 你也是英雄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.30,0:23:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.67,0:23:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}算了吧 英雄什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.09,0:23:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}我只是随处可见的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.93,0:23:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}平凡的驭兽使
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.80,0:23:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}不不不…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.47,0:23:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}大 大家为什么异口同声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.10,0:23:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}雷因果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.23,0:23:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}就是雷因呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.90,0:23:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.49,0:23:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}{\fad(100,100)}下集 大家的家
